Detailed Description

Feature object.

Description:

This object is set up for use within and by a FC_FeatureGroup -- it's not really set up to be used on it's own. Stores ids of ROI's (indices into a feature group's ROI list). Stores ids of the child & parent IDs of the feature.

Modifications:

  • FEB-18-2003 W Koegler Created
